{"tid":1566993,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"（靈異台）831死亡人仕尋人 quote from facebook, 大家去睇埋留言","createTime":"2019-09-14T00:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T19:50:04.000Z","uid":294275,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e48a92150cdf07df511971e0fd6c417d6e373463","tid":1566993,"uid":294275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T00:08:17.000Z","msg":"本人廢中一名，苦覓連登朋友不果，希望有心人可轉發<br />\n(以下係家人親身經歷)<br />\n<br />\nSubject: 831死亡人仕<br />\n<br />\n一位超高靈，但冇任何法力人仕平凡人，在今日（12/9）喺太子站「見」到嘅女亡靈，頭部大量流血😭<br />\n以下資料<br />\n<br />\n亡者：陳泳霖(或同音)<br />\n約19歲，約高168cm,<br />\n瘦身材(約110磅)，長直髮齊蔭，大眼睛<br />\n住大埔，<br />\n讀天主教學校或信仰係天主教(因只聽到「天主教」尼3個字<br />\n<br />\n事發時穿黑衫，戴黑幼框眼鏡，藍色運動褲，黑色Reebok,黑色腰包<br />\n<br />\n如各位認識尼個名字，請確認831後是否尚在，吾排除好多同名同姓，確認左尚在可安心，假若真係失蹤，定必要為亡者討回公道<br />\n<br />\n2019年9月12日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/211597766316250/permalink/541195840023106/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F211597766316250%2Fpermalink%2F541195840023106%2F&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88jcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=0160f281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/211597766316250/permalink/541195840023106/</a>"},{"pid":"8099d07f4dc02a469c48e222b593d366f8265e98","tid":1566993,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T00:12:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱有人開咗po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49ef166bebdc43253753631985a8f0a7b8d5740","tid":1566993,"uid":12612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:38:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"633b25a7a5fc51e46808621a492865e6807057aa","tid":1566993,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b8da3593b57677f36e545a88b42bf3f41f44c1","tid":1566993,"uid":79463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,